    <briefdescription>
<para>Live scan metrics collected during a table scan operation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds named <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Counter" kindref="compound">Counter</ref> and <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Timer" kindref="compound">Timer</ref> instances obtained from a <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1MetricsContext" kindref="compound">MetricsContext</ref>. Call <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1ScanMetrics_1a225cd53e1bf609f31e739cc6eb465880" kindref="member">Make()</ref> at the start of a scan to obtain an instrumented instance, then increment counters and start/stop the planning timer as the scan proceeds. Call <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1ScanMetrics_1aceaf909e93eb63ad83fa613ac4daa588" kindref="member">ToResult()</ref> at the end to obtain the serialisable <ref refid="structiceberg_1_1ScanMetricsResult" kindref="compound">ScanMetricsResult</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
